'''亚当·沙拉拉'''（Adham Sharara，{{bd|1953年|3月24日||}}）是一名[[加拿大|加拿大]]体育人物，生于[[开罗|开罗]]。1999年至2014年担任[[国际乒联|国际乒联]]主席<ref>Bernd Ulrich Gross, Werner Schlager Table Tennis: Tips from a World Champion  2011 - Page 164 "Do you really believe that table tennis may become a "big sport" like the ITTF President Adham Sharara always maintains? Table tennis is already a big sport in some countries. To reach the world stage, all have to work with professionals, ."</ref><ref>Beijing Review - Volume 44, Issues 1-26 - Page 257 2001 "International Table Tennis Federation President Adham Sharara said on May 6 the sport would become "boring" if China continued to dominate every event, as they did at the world championships in Osaka and at the 1996 and 2000 Olympic"</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=ITTF Executive Committee (EC) |url=http://www.ittf.com/_front_page/ittf2.asp?category=directory_e |publisher=ITTF |accessdate=21 March 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160904230922/http://www.ittf.com/_front_page/ittf2.asp?category=directory_e |archivedate=2016-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年4月28日在东京当选新设立的职位—"Chairman of the ITTF"<ref>{{cite web|title=Adham Sharara elected to the new position of ITTF Chairman|url=http://www.ittf.com/media/press_release/PR_30Apr14/index.html|publisher=ITTF|work=ITTF Press Release|date=28 April 2014|accessdate=21 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612054646/http://www.ittf.com/media/press_release/PR_30apr14/index.html|archive-date=2015-06-12|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=ITTF Directory - Officials - Chairman|url=http://www.ittf.com/ittf_invoices/Chairman.asp|publisher=ITTF|accessdate=21 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423045007/http://ittf.com/ittf_invoices/Chairman.asp|archive-date=2015-04-23|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年国际乒联宣布发现他在任期内违反职责，被停权四年<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ittf.com/2019/03/15/ittf-executive-committee-statement-former-president-mr-adham-sharara/ |title=ITTF Executive Committee statement on former President Mr Adham Sharara |access-date=2020-07-01 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516180333/https://www.ittf.com/2019/03/15/ittf-executive-committee-statement-former-president-mr-adham-sharara/ }}</ref>。

